Like we were like. you know. fuck yeah.

847
00:31:47.697 --> 00:31:50.366
Like... one of the happiest moments

848
00:31:50.700 --> 00:31:53.244
that we had during the whole event.

849
00:31:53.453 --> 00:31:54.745
Nick and I.

