00:32:12.221 --> 00:32:14.724
through that shouldn't have gotten through.

863
00:32:15.183 --> 00:32:17.602
And so we're being thorough.

864
00:32:17.852 --> 00:32:20.647
And we were talking to one of the

865
00:32:21.314 --> 00:32:22.607
government representatives

866
00:32:23.942 --> 00:32:25.108
who is the regional

867
00:32:25.109 --> 00:32:27.027
representative for that agency.

