00:32:27.028 --> 00:32:28.904
Calls are going up chains of command.

869
00:32:28.905 --> 00:32:30.698
and ultimately

870
00:32:31.115 --> 00:32:32.157
the full bird Colonel

871
00:32:32.158 --> 00:32:35.244
who is in charge of the base arrives on...

872
00:32:36.037 --> 00:32:38.164
on scene at Black Gate.

873
00:32:46.130 --> 00:32:48.799
And he just makes the call.

874
00:32:48.800 --> 00:32:50.592
"Turn everybody around...

875
00:32:50.593 --> 00:32:52.260
put everybody back out...

876
00:32:52.261 --> 00:32:53.679
I don't care who they are."

877
00:32:53.680 --> 00:32:55.514
Tim calls on the SAT phone.

878
00:32:55.515 --> 00:32:56.974
He's like. they're kicking them out.

879
00:32:56.975 --> 00:32:58.350
They're going to kick them all out.

880
00:32:58.351 --> 00:32:59.518
I got a message from Sean Lee

881
00:32:59.519 --> 00:33:02.145
that says a colonel from the 82nd

882
00:33:02.146 --> 00:33:03.230
is seriously about to kick out

883
00:33:03.231 --> 00:33:05.190
300 orphans

884
00:33:05.191 --> 00:33:07.652
and Christians and American citizens.

885
00:33:27.755 --> 00:33:30.048
G... tried to talk sense into them.

886
00:33:30.049 --> 00:33:32.551
Can we at least go through all these people

887
00:33:32.552 --> 00:33:33.511
and make sure we pull out

888
00:33:33.512 --> 00:33:34.761
the American citizens

889
00:33:34.762 --> 00:33:36.513
and the green card holders?

890
00:33:36.514 --> 00:33:37.473
Pump the brakes here.

891
00:33:37.474 --> 00:33:39.234
Let's talk about this.
And he's like. "Nope.

892
00:33:40.435 --> 00:33:41.060
It's my decision.

893
00:33:41.060 --> 00:33:41.561
It's a command."

894
00:33:41.562 --> 00:33:44.104
Like. well. I'm not in the military.

895
00:33:44.105 --> 00:33:45.856
I'm not here for the military.

896
00:33:45.857 --> 00:33:47.900
And that's not really a lawful order.

897
00:33:47.942 --> 00:33:49.318
Let's talk about this.

898
00:34:07.086 --> 00:34:08.587
Like. is this an unlawful order

899
00:34:08.588 --> 00:34:11.424
or is he just a terrible human being?

900
00:34:11.591 --> 00:34:12.591
What is happening?

901
00:34:12.675 --> 00:34:16.053
From his perspective.
even though Tim wasn't

902
00:34:16.054 --> 00:34:16.971
the team leader.

903
00:34:16.972 --> 00:34:18.973
Tim was the only guy that he knew.

904
00:34:24.312 --> 00:34:26.898
He thought. "This is some fuckin' guy

905
00:34:28.274 --> 00:34:31.444
that's just showing up in Afghanistan

906
00:34:32.070 --> 00:34:34.071
running seven buses in.

907
00:34:34.072 --> 00:34:34.447
you know.

908
00:34:34.448 --> 00:34:36.656
fuck this guy. I want to kick him out."

909
00:34:36.657 --> 00:34:38.992
These were people that fought

910
00:34:38.993 --> 00:34:41.120
and had their relatives die for us.

911
00:34:41.370 --> 00:34:42.829
They lost their limbs for us.

912
00:34:42.830 --> 00:34:45.500
They lost their adult lives and youth and

913
00:34:46.042 --> 00:34:47.627
their innocence for us.

914
00:34:48.127 --> 00:34:49.461
Yes. they're fighting for Afghanistan.

915
00:34:49.462 --> 00:34:50.837
Yes. they're fighting for their people.

916
00:34:50.838 --> 00:34:52.672
But they are fighting with us.

917
00:34:52.673 --> 00:34:53.633
That's who... that's who

918
00:34:53.634 --> 00:34:55.342
we're trying to save here.

919
00:34:55.343 --> 00:34:57.887
From our perspective.

920
00:34:58.471 --> 00:35:01.849
this was possibly the most valuable load

921
00:35:02.058 --> 00:35:06.104
of people we had brought in thus far.

922
00:35:11.901 --> 00:35:13.527
I said. Hey. look. I'm

923
00:35:13.528 --> 00:35:14.278
a West Pointer too.

924
00:35:14.279 --> 00:35:15.403
I've been to your school.

925
00:35:15.404 --> 00:35:15.988
Trust me on this.

926
00:35:15.989 --> 00:35:17.447
We have the manifest for you.

927
00:35:17.448 --> 00:35:19.528
He said. "I don't care
where you've been to school".

928
00:35:23.329 --> 00:35:24.538
But the next decision he made

929
00:35:24.539 --> 00:35:26.081
was just unconscionable.

930
00:35:26.082 --> 00:35:28.375
It embarrassed me for the Army.

931
00:35:28.376 --> 00:35:29.960
If I have somebody with a blue passport.

932
00:35:29.961 --> 00:35:30.670
if I have an American

933
00:35:30.671 --> 00:35:32.295
hold up a blue passport.

934
00:35:32.296 --> 00:35:33.755
can that person get on a bus?

935
00:35:33.756 --> 00:35:35.090
If I have somebody hold up

936
00:35:35.091 --> 00:35:36.383
an SIV.

937
00:35:36.384 --> 00:35:37.884
a special immigration visa.

938
00:35:37.885 --> 00:35:39.678
can that person get back on the bus?

939
00:35:39.679 --> 00:35:41.722
If I have a P1. if I have a green card.

940
00:35:42.223 --> 00:35:44.141
I have a spouse of an American citizen...

941
00:35:44.142 --> 00:35:45.976
can these people get
back on these buses?

942
00:35:45.977 --> 00:35:47.978
"No. I don't care who they are.

943
00:35:47.979 --> 00:35:49.104
You get back on those buses

944
00:35:49.105 --> 00:35:50.897
and those buses go back into Kabul.

945
00:35:50.898 --> 00:35:51.940
Get them off this base."

946
00:35:51.941 --> 00:35:53.943
Can we just keep the blue passport holders?

947
00:35:54.110 --> 00:35:55.152
Tim yells.

948
00:35:55.153 --> 00:35:56.486
And he says.

949
00:35:56.487 --> 00:35:58.530
"Everybody goes back on these buses

950
00:35:58.531 --> 00:36:00.700
and I want them escorted
back off the base."

951
00:36:01.409 --> 00:36:03.452
And the colonel said. kick them out.

952
00:36:52.627 --> 00:36:53.877
Whoever just made the decision

953
00:36:53.878 --> 00:36:54.754
to turn his bus around

954
00:36:54.755 --> 00:36:56.004
essentially just killed...

955
00:36:56.005 --> 00:36:57.714
Just murdered... these people.

956
00:36:57.715 --> 00:37:00.009
And by the way. some of those people

957
00:37:00.885 --> 00:37:01.968
are children

958
00:37:01.969 --> 00:37:03.261
and some of these people were women.

959
00:37:03.262 --> 00:37:05.096
But some of these people are Americans

960
00:37:05.097 --> 00:37:07.642
that we just sent back to the Taliban.

961
00:37:08.100 --> 00:37:09.684
Whoever got killed by the Taliban

962
00:37:09.685 --> 00:37:10.811
because of that decision.

963
00:37:11.854 --> 00:37:13.813
that decision was on him.

964
00:37:13.814 --> 00:37:16.483
And I called Senator Tillis.

965
00:37:16.484 --> 00:37:19.903
Senator Tillis called multiple generals.

966
00:37:19.904 --> 00:37:21.780
Those generals called to the ground.

967
00:37:21.781 --> 00:37:22.864
But by the time

968
00:37:22.865 --> 00:37:24.157
the generals connected

969
00:37:24.158 --> 00:37:26.868
with the colonel to stop it.

970
00:37:26.869 --> 00:37:30.206
he had already kicked the buses off.

971
00:37:31.832 --> 00:37:34.085
And we... we did not see them again.

972
00:37:35.044 --> 00:37:37.004
Every Taliban

973
00:37:37.380 --> 00:37:38.546
around the airport

974
00:37:38.547 --> 00:37:40.590
saw them come through the gate

975
00:37:40.591 --> 00:37:42.843
on a bus with Americans

976
00:37:43.719 --> 00:37:46.846
and now every Taliban member

977
00:37:46.847 --> 00:37:49.432
at the gate was going to see them leave

978
00:37:49.433 --> 00:37:51.017
and go back into Kabul.

979
00:37:51.018 --> 00:37:52.602
And that's heart wrenching.

980
00:37:52.603 --> 00:37:55.730
There's not enough emotional capacity left

981
00:37:55.731 --> 00:37:58.734
in my soul to be able to mourn

982
00:37:59.402 --> 00:38:02.113
four busloads of people
that are about to die.

983
00:38:03.531 --> 00:38:06.533
Because the time spent in anguish

984
00:38:06.534 --> 00:38:08.285
and mourning. is time

985
00:38:08.286 --> 00:38:09.494
that could have been spent

986
00:38:09.495 --> 00:38:10.912
trying to save other people.

987
00:38:10.913 --> 00:38:12.414
We continued to do what we had to do

988
00:38:12.415 --> 00:38:12.957
because we knew these

989
00:38:12.957 --> 00:38:13.791
people were counting on us.

990
00:38:13.792 --> 00:38:15.834
We knew that the guys.

991
00:38:15.835 --> 00:38:16.752
our friends

992
00:38:16.753 --> 00:38:18.461
who were at HKIA trying to help

993
00:38:18.462 --> 00:38:20.464
people needed us to do this work.

994
00:38:21.007 --> 00:38:23.425
The Afghans trying to get into HKIA

995
00:38:23.426 --> 00:38:24.551
needed us to do this work.

996
00:38:24.552 --> 00:38:27.178
So we put it behind us and put our noses

997
00:38:27.179 --> 00:38:29.180
the grindstone and continued working.

998
00:38:29.181 --> 00:38:30.933
And we worked for the rest of that day.

999
00:38:51.996 --> 00:38:53.789
The guys.

1000
00:38:54.123 --> 00:38:56.542
unwilling to quit.

1001
00:38:56.792 --> 00:38:58.919
tripled their efforts and worked

1002
00:39:00.046 --> 00:39:03.382
and pulled out hundreds
more people that night.

1003
00:39:15.811 --> 00:39:18.856
Everything is starting to collapse on HKIA.

1004
00:39:19.440 --> 00:39:20.648
People are breaking down.

1005
00:39:20.649 --> 00:39:22.192
people are loading up.

1006
00:39:22.193 --> 00:39:23.777
they're taking bulldozers

1007
00:39:23.778 --> 00:39:25.320
and driving them over night vision.

1008
00:39:25.321 --> 00:39:26.946
You see Marines with sledgehammers

1009
00:39:26.947 --> 00:39:28.156
going into aircraft

1010
00:39:28.157 --> 00:39:30.951
and starting to smash
control panels to aircraft.

1011
00:40:04.985 --> 00:40:06.653
Like. everything is starting to crumble

1012
00:40:06.654 --> 00:40:09.532
and fall back to like this last Alamo.

1013
00:40:09.782 --> 00:40:12.283
The only thing staying out is security.

1014
00:40:12.284 --> 00:40:13.868
And one of those security checkpoints

1015
00:40:13.869 --> 00:40:15.328
is at the Abbey Gate.

1016
00:40:15.329 --> 00:40:15.996
And the Abbey Gate

1017
00:40:15.997 --> 00:40:18.790
was one of the few places where

1018
00:40:18.791 --> 00:40:20.376
if you had all the documentation.

1019
00:40:21.627 --> 00:40:23.461
the American government would

1020
00:40:23.462 --> 00:40:24.963
vet and proof you there.

1021
00:40:24.964 --> 00:40:26.506
And if you were on their list.

1022
00:40:26.507 --> 00:40:28.133
you could come through that gate.

1023
00:40:28.134 --> 00:40:30.093
There are offshoots.

1024
00:40:30.094 --> 00:40:32.095
factions of the Taliban.

1025
00:40:32.096 --> 00:40:33.388
Name them whatever you want.

1026
00:40:33.389 --> 00:40:35.014
ISIS-K. I don't care what you call them.

1027
00:40:35.015 --> 00:40:37.226
It's the Taliban. It's just factions.

1028
00:40:37.518 --> 00:40:39.394
They're pragmatically organized.

1029
00:40:39.395 --> 00:40:42.481
So the Taliban sent in a suicide bomber

1030
00:40:43.023 --> 00:40:45.693
to that gate. an IED. and... um...

1031
00:40:48.696 --> 00:40:49.780
blew it up.

1032
00:40:57.788 --> 00:40:59.998
The attack took place at Hamid Karzai

1033
00:40:59.999 --> 00:41:02.585
International Airport
in Kabul. Afghanistan.

1034
00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:04.586
As a result of this attack.

1035
00:41:04.587 --> 00:41:07.756
13 of our nation's best and brightest.

1036
00:41:08.424 --> 00:41:09.674
our heroes

1037
00:41:09.675 --> 00:41:11.426
paid the ultimate sacrifice

1038
00:41:11.427 --> 00:41:12.552
in an effort to save the lives

1039
00:41:12.553 --> 00:41:14.053
of American citizens

1040
00:41:14.054 --> 00:41:15.930
and thousands of Afghans

1041
00:41:15.931 --> 00:41:18.517
during the Non Combatant
Evacuation of HKIA.

1042
00:43:04.415 --> 00:43:06.499
There's so much of their life

1043
00:43:06.500 --> 00:43:09.252
that is left to be lived.

1044
00:43:09.253 --> 00:43:11.004
So many things they haven't experienced.

1045
00:43:11.005 --> 00:43:12.380
So many things they don't know.

1046
00:43:12.381 --> 00:43:14.424
They haven't been married.
they haven't had children.

1047
00:43:14.425 --> 00:43:15.800
They haven't traveled the world.

1048
00:43:15.801 --> 00:43:16.801
They haven't.

1049
00:43:17.344 --> 00:43:19.972
you know. found what they're good at.

1050
00:43:20.306 --> 00:43:22.308
They... there's so much they don't know.

1051
00:43:22.891 --> 00:43:23.891
And... uh...

1052
00:43:24.602 --> 00:43:25.893
you know. and now they're gone.

1053
00:43:25.894 --> 00:43:28.647
And they were all kids. 13 kids. you know.

1054
00:43:28.981 --> 00:43:30.898
You know. they were out there

1055
00:43:30.899 --> 00:43:35.112
helping people. you
know. giving people aid.

1056
00:43:35.821 --> 00:43:37.906
helping people get through the wire.

1057
00:43:38.699 --> 00:43:41.367
trying to do the right thing.

1058
00:43:41.368 --> 00:43:44.787
trying to represent. you know. themselves.

1059
00:43:44.788 --> 00:43:45.581
the country.

1060
00:43:45.582 --> 00:43:47.915
the military in the
best way possible. like.

1061
00:43:47.916 --> 00:43:48.959
you know. just

1062
00:43:49.710 --> 00:43:52.421
absolute heroes.

1063
00:44:04.642 --> 00:44:05.975
We knew that we would not be able

1064
00:44:05.976 --> 00:44:07.435
to send another flight in

1065
00:44:07.436 --> 00:44:08.270
and we wouldn't be able

1066
00:44:08.271 --> 00:44:09.646
to get anybody else out.

1067
00:44:09.647 --> 00:44:12.650
When the last airplane lifted out of HKIA

1068
00:44:13.025 --> 00:44:15.319
at the end of August. That was their hope.

1069
00:44:16.320 --> 00:44:17.904
The United States ended its

1070
00:44:17.905 --> 00:44:20.157
20 year war in Afghanistan today

1071
00:44:20.366 --> 00:44:21.325
with the conclusion

1072
00:44:21.326 --> 00:44:23.076
of the largest noncombatant

1073
00:44:23.077 --> 00:44:24.952
airlift in American history.

1074
00:44:24.953 --> 00:44:28.289
I remember at one point Sean G

1075
00:44:28.290 --> 00:44:31.250
was still sending me names

1076
00:44:31.251 --> 00:44:32.711
and this was like

1077
00:44:32.795 --> 00:44:35.171
right around the time we were learning that

1078
00:44:35.172 --> 00:44:36.631
this would not be possible any more.

1079
00:44:36.632 --> 00:44:37.966
And he said.

1080
00:44:38.801 --> 00:44:40.927
"We have to keep making a list.

1081
00:44:40.928 --> 00:44:43.638
And this is going to
be a list of the people

1082
00:44:43.639 --> 00:44:45.556
that we were forced to leave behind."

1083
00:44:45.557 --> 00:44:48.102
And it just felt so haunting to

1084
00:44:49.061 --> 00:44:51.771
put their names in these spreadsheets.

1085
00:44:51.772 --> 00:44:54.400
knowing that we would have all kept going

1086
00:44:55.067 --> 00:44:56.109
as long as we were able.

1087
00:44:56.110 --> 00:44:57.777
And the choice was taken away.

1088
00:44:57.778 --> 00:44:59.696
And we just thought. we had more time.

1089
00:44:59.697 --> 00:45:00.656
We're waiting on the ramp.

1090
00:45:00.657 --> 00:45:02.365
The four of us are at the very back

1091
00:45:02.366 --> 00:45:03.616
with the air crew.

1092
00:45:03.617 --> 00:45:05.702
And as the ramp closes

1093
00:45:05.703 --> 00:45:07.705
and the last little bit of light

1094
00:45:09.248 --> 00:45:11.749
from Afghanistan finally

1095
00:45:11.750 --> 00:45:13.335
closes out.

1096
00:45:13.585 --> 00:45:14.585
it's...

1097
00:45:16.922 --> 00:45:19.883
It's like this resounding gong of failure.

1098
00:45:20.426 --> 00:45:22.677
I'm surrounded by hundreds of people.

1099
00:45:22.678 --> 00:45:23.262
We had a...

1100
00:45:23.263 --> 00:45:26.014
we had a woman that started fainting.

1101
00:45:26.765 --> 00:45:28.725
Is there a doctor here?

1102
00:45:28.726 --> 00:45:30.893
14 people stand up.

1103
00:45:30.894 --> 00:45:33.104
All of them speak perfect English.

1104
00:45:33.105 --> 00:45:34.064
All of them have worked

1105
00:45:34.065 --> 00:45:36.149
for the Americans as doctors.

1106
00:45:36.150 --> 00:45:37.859
orthodontists. dentists.

1107
00:45:37.860 --> 00:45:39.235
and orthopedic surgeons

1108
00:45:39.236 --> 00:45:40.570
and open heart surgeons.

1109
00:45:40.571 --> 00:45:42.155
like they're on this plane.

1110
00:45:42.156 --> 00:45:43.740
That's who's on these planes.

1111
00:45:43.741 --> 00:45:45.241
These were amazing.

1112
00:45:45.242 --> 00:45:46.993
educated. hard working people

1113
00:45:46.994 --> 00:45:48.953
that worked and fought with Americans.

1114
00:45:48.954 --> 00:45:50.037
What our government did.

1115
00:45:50.038 --> 00:45:51.914
the decisions our government did

1116
00:45:51.915 --> 00:45:53.916
cost American lives.

